{"tid":656832,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"招兼職，觀塘入信封，即日出糧","createTime":"2018-05-07T14:26:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-07T15:52:44.000Z","uid":77192,"like":2,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"e07cf43aba40fc3c811dde24efa8d69d90ae9f91","tid":656832,"uid":77192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T14:26:16.000Z","msg":"各位巴打絲打 <br />\n<br />\nHK$ 50/ hour，午飯時間不計鐘 <br />\n<br />\n8/5,9/5 招人入信封，慈善機構信，三至五名 <br />\n<br />\n冷氣房工作，可聽歌，手唔好停就得，小心守時有責任感 <br />\n<br />\n觀塘工作（地鐵站旁），時間上午九點至下午六點，午飯時間一點到兩點，可彈性十時到或五時走，夠六個小時就可以 <br />\n<br />\n付款，銀行過數／Payme／現金，跟上次經驗，今次一早準備定錢，費事又有人講三講四 <br />\n<br />\n有興趣者，TG: gornine911"},{"pid":"8774c7868a272a74823ccc1fd8ed99a09eb4ea02","tid":656832,"uid":147292,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T14:38:33.000Z","msg":"起碼都60啦"},{"pid":"cc233641c46a6d8aa5762277dc5bc9d22a203b7a","tid":656832,"uid":61398,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T14:40:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b61ce51fe8f053159d8c289ddcd5a7c517170a7c","tid":656832,"uid":34470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T14:40:49.000Z","msg":"我收40就得"},{"pid":"22a0e60df691a0100396fe7a32c2dfd7ae247685","tid":656832,"uid":37021,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b61ce51fe8f053159d8c289ddcd5a7c517170a7c","tid":656832,"uid":34470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T14:40:49.000Z","msg":"我收40就得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T14:41:36.000Z","msg":"倒貼40 求樓主俾我返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c96e2d194a7ad72f557d78921344af94856c35c","tid":656832,"uid":108266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T14:42:13.000Z","msg":"郵政著揀信組入下信65蚊一粒鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07833a312ba0b3e20caaf80ec4336a1aad2c7664","tid":656832,"uid":138858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c96e2d194a7ad72f557d7892134